{"tid":1536887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好講「黑社會」，要講「黑警殺人」","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:49:13.000Z","uid":39316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b785e5094a5b99df9d7102e7e8984bb2241b18f6","tid":1536887,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"睇到有幾個黑警圍住個無知覺既手足，眾目睽睽下無視手足可能係斷頸椎既危險，大幅度郁佢個頭<br />\n而且夾硬拉佢變坐係度既姿態，意圖令個畫面好睇d，唔係有人訓左係地完全無郁，仲要拖手足走，不過拍片影低曬啦屌你老味<br />\n<br />\n之後人群開始圍住班黑警，叫佢地做「黑社會」。但個人認為個畫面唔夠力量。<span style=\"color: gold;\">當時d黑警個個做左虧心事咁驚青，我認為最能夠點出佢地內心驚青既野先會令佢地更無所遁形</span>、更加唔知點做好、而且會形成更有力量既畫面。<br />\n<br />\n以後如果見手足無知覺（當然希望千祈唔好有事，多一個都嫌多），希望大家大叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警殺人</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4b83a451c9bf46f7003270f6820ac18fa6e6245","tid":1536887,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:46:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />